{"tid":2471060,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人玩outrider？","createTime":"2021-04-01T09:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T20:37:13.000Z","uid":249378,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"894d10963d654b49b79e26686d0ea7b8ba8170ba","tid":2471060,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"第三人稱射擊+異能打寶驚(1-3人)，類似Division、broderland、destiny<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNvVCBqnddVxaj9ruCeU3m8qYoho94AeshJujHKwoQiNX?filename=eeZ71ZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeZ71ZY.jpg&h=b3251a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nhardware requirement:<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma75evRatsDumc1Mjf2M9vYMwewnX6SJfqxLf3JB5hAkp?filename=95y44dK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95y44dK.png&h=02c5f6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以三人組隊，序章之後有四種職業：技術士（遠攻）、火法師(中攻)、騙術師(近戰)和破壞者(坦)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme2z3HH3ywAEP67RPd3rNsNhdqKJh2JZhjuh7mMW1RSHx?filename=KjwKjX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjwKjX4.jpg&h=c4e0183c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n技能樹圖，後期會有三個流派<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbwg7bSrnBgyvy4KuX2DS1pN7bhoiJeqmPF9P8TLtZJ5Q?filename=byBuv2X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyBuv2X.jpg&h=2b12ab16&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n主動技只可以裝四個，有cd限制<br />\n四個職業都有相應技回血，所以唔洗有人專玩補血職業<br />\n因為開發商出過Gears of War，所以射擊會有Gears of War feel<br />\n<br />\n收集品：<br />\n皮革&ndash;通過殺死敵對動物或拆除盔甲獲得<br />\n鐵&ndash;開採礦脈或拆除武器<br />\n鈦&ndash;拆除史詩或傳奇物品，或從敵人和礦脈中掉落的稀有液<br />\n異常碎片（詞條）&ndash;通過拆解物品獲得<br />\n<br />\n刷位：裝備同詞條<br />\n詞條對應四個職業出，詞條可以拆去其他槍，唔會anthem咁狙屬性放係手槍咁on9<br />\n<br />\n玩完demo暫時吸引點係故事寫得唔錯,<br />\n缺點：整人樣太普通,有d政治正確、掩護判定有d謎<br />\n<br />\ndemo會inherit存檔所以好多痴線佬會sl大法每日刷裝<br />\n<br />\nrelease date：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSpjRcnBkbe7vsGfNSqZpdSCXtpnv1DJ4xuf2WfBJoWWy?filename=kn3s1YS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkn3s1YS.jpg&h=e450ecfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對應反香港時間係4月2號12點<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVBxREerBGsy2G3QaYvQbskyLnPCQZPFgC78qZRjA8abD?filename=tQ1RKaW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQ1RKaW.png&h=d203e38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nrelease date即上xgp,反向宣傳xgp<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcPetrghiC5ePBEnU6c9hzaenK2iTBF9wojjs5HFEyEbH?filename=1jYAroW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jYAroW.png&h=b2c7e2c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nxgp頭一個月10蚊抵到爛"},{"pid":"8375a30a224fb37bc848f92afd0c524c1dd32b5c","tid":2471060,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"已經有得下載啦   xgp上架啦"},{"pid":"2f6a473d04394950d412974cae2a1dc2d1c7df63","tid":2471060,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8375a30a224fb37bc848f92afd0c524c1dd32b5c","tid":2471060,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"已經有得下載啦   xgp上架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T09:20:10.000Z","msg":"主機又偷跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f86cae30b0067d21e654cc90b44ec9b6508859","tid":2471060,"uid":28853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f6a473d04394950d412974cae2a1dc2d1c7df63","tid":2471060,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8375a30a224fb37bc848f92afd0c524c1dd32b5c","tid":2471060,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"已經有得下載啦   xgp上架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T09:20:10.000Z","msg":"主機又偷跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-01T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"係, 已用App Download左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"h